🚀 Terraform Three-Tier Architecture Project
📌 Project Overview

This project implements a Three-Tier Architecture on AWS using Terraform.

The architecture is divided into:

Frontend Layer (Web Tier)
Backend Layer (Application Tier)
Database Layer (RDS Tier)

It follows Infrastructure as Code (IaC) principles using reusable Terraform modules.

🏗️ Architecture Diagram (Conceptual)
Internet
   ↓
Frontend ALB
   ↓
Frontend EC2 (Auto Scaling)
   ↓
Backend ALB
   ↓
Backend EC2 (Auto Scaling)
   ↓
RDS (MySQL Database)
